snippet.title: Helms of Fury - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Helms of Fury is an action roguelike coming to Kickstarter on Oct 21!  Featuring big pixels, crazy abilities, intense combat, and hugely replayable procedural levels.  Follow us on Kickstarter for updates on our campaign!

Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/abitawake/helms-of-fury
Website: https://helmsoffury.com/
